{{md-parallax image="/assets/images/legion-2560x1440-wide.jpg"}}
<div id="home" class="section grey darken-4 white-text">
  <div class="row container">
    <h1>No Breaks</h1>
    <p>
      We are a raiding guild on Thrall (9/13 Mythic HFC). Although we're not
      hardcore raiders, we buckle down when necessary. No Breaks prides itself
      on creating a close-knit community and friendly, albeit weird, members.
      We have a guild leader that isn't a scrub and we wear pink on Fridays!
    </p>

    <h2>Plans for Legion</h2>
    <p>
      No Breaks will be raiding in Legion! We are looking for some new members
      to fill out our current raid team and help us with progression when the
      new expansion drops.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="row container crying-bear">
    crying bear placeholder
  </div>
</div>

{{md-parallax image="/assets/images/emerald-nightmare.jpg"}}
<div id="raiding" class="section blue-grey white-text">
  <div class="row container">
      <h1>Raiding</h1>
      <p>Did we mention we raid? Check out our progress, laugh at our logs, and watch us on Twitch!</p>
      <br>
      {{#link-to 'raiding' tagName='button' class='btn cyan'}}
        {{link-to 'Raiding' 'raiding'}}
      {{/link-to}}
  </div>
</div>

